title: Dishwasher COUNTERTOP BRACKET
description: Dishwasher COUNTERTOP BRACKET PartSelect Number PS16219683 Manufacturer Part Number WD01X27759 This countertop bracket is an OEM replacement part specially designed for dishwashers. The bracket is made from stainless steel, and it is responsible for securing the top edge of the dishwasher to the underside of the kitchen countertop. This safety mechanism keeps the dishwasher safe and prevents injury to users by preventing the dishwasher from tipping forward whenever the door is opened or closed. Each countertop bracket is sold individually, therefore, ensure you have ordered the correct amount for your dishwasher. Mounting hardware is sold separately.
